              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-7 h-7 text-[#D97706] group-hover:text-white transition-colors" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-extrabold text-[#1a1f36] mb-2">15-Min Response</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Our team responds to every enquiry within 15 minutes during operating hours.</p>
